 @dev This contract allows testing distribution with custom addresses

@notice Confirm a transaction

 @param txId Transaction ID
@notice Check if address is owner
@notice Get transaction details
@notice Check if owner confirmed transaction

@dev Адресите се взимат от Addresses.sol - ЕДИН ФАЙЛ ЗА ВСИЧКО!
 
      CONTROL SYSTEM (v39):
        Normal Functions (Owner OR Exempt Slots can call):
          - pause/unpause trading
          - blacklist users
          - propose/execute mints
          - update exempt slots (if not locked)
          - update DEX addresses (if not locked)
          - update liquidity pairs (if not locked)
          - lockDEXAddresses() - Lock router/factory
          - lockExemptSlots() - Lock exempt slots
          - lockLiquidityPairs() - Lock liquidity pairs
 
        UNLOCK Functions (ONLY Multi-Sig can call):
          - unlockDEXAddresses() - Unlock router/factory (ONLY multi-sig)
          - unlockExemptSlots() - Unlock exempt slots (ONLY multi-sig)
          - unlockLiquidityPairs() - Unlock pairs (ONLY multi-sig)
          - REQUIRES 3-of-5 multi-sig signatures
 
      MULTI-SIG INDEPENDENCE:
        - Multi-sig owners CAN be different from exempt slots
        - Multi-sig address MUST be added as exempt slot to work
        - Example: 5 multi-sig owners control unlock operations
                   4 different exempt slots control normal operations
 
      FEES: 0.08% total (0.03% burn + 0.05% owner)
      - Applied when at least one party is normal user
      - SAME fee for ALL cases (normal and Exempt Slot → Normal)
 
      NORMAL USERS:
        ✓ Can trade (buy/sell) through Router
        ✗ CANNOT add/remove liquidity directly to Pair
        ✓ 0.08% fees on all transactions
        ✓ 2,000 token max per transaction
        ✓ 2 hour cooldown
        ✓ 4,000 token max wallet
      
      EXEMPT SLOTS (owner + eAddr1-4) ↔ EXEMPT/Router/Factory:
        ✓ NO fees (0%)
        ✓ NO limits
        ✓ CAN add/remove liquidity
        ✓ CAN control contract functions
 
      SPECIAL: EXEMPT SLOTS (owner + eAddr1-4) → NORMAL user:
        ⚠️ Owner ALSO follows these rules!
        ✓ 0.08% fees (SAME as normal!)
        ✓ 100 token max (not 2000!)
        ✓ 24 hour cooldown (not 2 hours!)
 
      LOCKING:
        - Exempt 4 slots: CAN be locked forever
        - Router/Factory: CAN be locked forever (v38)
        - Liquidity Pairs: CAN be locked forever
 
      DEPLOYMENT:
        - Total Supply: 100,000,000 tokens
        - DEV Wallet: 96,000,000 tokens (for liquidity + reserve)
        - Contract: 4,000,000 tokens (for distribution)
        - After distribution:
          • Marketing: 1,500,000
          • Team: 1,000,000
          • Advisor: 1,500,000
        - Hardhat (chainid 31337): Deployer gets tokens
        - BSC Testnet (chainid 97): Testnet wallets
        - BSC Mainnet (chainid 56): Real wallets
 
      EXEMPT SLOTS:
        - Automatically set to distribution addresses
        - eAddr1 = DEV wallet
        - eAddr2 = Marketing wallet
        - eAddr3 = Team wallet
        - eAddr4 = Advisor wallet
        - ALL 5 addresses (owner + 4 slots) have equal control
 
      ADDRESSES (hardcoded in constructor):
        See config/addresses.js for reference
        - Testnet: 0xCBfA..., 0x67eD..., 0xD1a7..., etc.
        - Mainnet: 0x567c..., 0x58ec..., 0x6300..., 0x8d95...

rFrom","outputs":[{"internalType":"bool","name":"","type":"bool"}],"stateMutability":"nonpayable","type":"function"}],"devdoc":{"author":"VMK","details":"\u0410\u0434\u0440\u0435\u0441\u0438\u0442\u0435 \u0441\u0435 \u0432\u0437\u0438\u043c\u0430\u0442 \u043e\u0442 Addresses.sol - \u0415\u0414\u0418\u041d \u0424\u0410\u0419\u041b \u0417\u0410 \u0412\u0421\u0418\u0427\u041a\u041e!       CONTROL SYSTEM (v39):        Normal Functions (Owner OR Exempt Slots can call):          - pause/unpause trading          - blacklist users          - propose/execute mints          - update exempt slots (if not locked)          - update DEX addresses (if not locked)          - update liquidity pairs (if not locked)          - lockDEXAddresses() - Lock router/factory          - lockExemptSlots() - Lock exempt slots          - lockLiquidityPairs() - Lock liquidity pairs         UNLOCK Functions (ONLY Multi-Sig can call):          - unlockDEXAddresses() - Unlock router/factory (ONLY multi-sig)          - unlockExemptSlots() - Unlock exempt slots (ONLY multi-sig)          - unlockLiquidityPairs() - Unlock pairs (ONLY multi-sig)          - REQUIRES 3-of-5 multi-sig signatures       MULTI-SIG INDEPENDENCE:        - Multi-sig owners CAN be different from exempt slots        - Multi-sig address MUST be added as exempt slot to work        - Example: 5 multi-sig owners control unlock operations                   4 different exempt slots control normal operations       FEES: 0.08% total (0.03% burn + 0.05% owner)      - Applied when at least one party is normal user      - SAME fee for ALL cases (normal and Exempt Slot \u2192 Normal)       NORMAL USERS:        \u2713 Can trade (buy/sell) through Router        \u2717 CANNOT add/remove liquidity directly to Pair        \u2713 0.08% fees on all transactions        \u2713 2,000 token max per transaction        \u2713 2 hour cooldown        \u2713 4,000 token max wallet            EXEMPT SLOTS (owner + eAddr1-4) \u2194 EXEMPT/Router/Factory:        \u2713 NO fees (0%)        \u2713 NO limits        \u2713 CAN add/remove liquidity        \u2713 CAN control contract functions       SPECIAL: EXEMPT SLOTS (owner + eAddr1-4) \u2192 NORMAL user:        \u26a0\ufe0f Owner ALSO follows these rules!        \u2713 0.08% fees (SAME as normal!)        \u2713 100 token max (not 2000!)        \u2713 24 hour cooldown (not 2 hours!)       LOCKING:        - Exempt 4 slots: CAN be locked forever        - Router/Factory: CAN be locked forever (v38)        - Liquidity Pairs: CAN be locked forever       DEPLOYMENT:        - Total Supply: 100,000,000 tokens        - DEV Wallet: 96,000,000 tokens (for liquidity + reserve)        - Contract: 4,000,000 tokens (for distribution)        - After distribution:          \u2022 Marketing: 1,500,000          \u2022 Team: 1,000,000          \u2022 Advisor: 1,500,000        - Hardhat (chainid 31337): Deployer gets tokens        - BSC Testnet (chainid 97): Testnet wallets        - BSC Mainnet (chainid 56): Real wallets       EXEMPT SLOTS:        - Automatically set to distribution addresses        - eAddr1 = DEV wallet        - eAddr2 = Marketing wallet        - eAddr3 = Team wallet        - eAddr4 = Advisor wallet        - ALL 5 addresses (owner + 4 slots) have equal control       ADDRESSES (hardcoded in constructor):        See config/addresses.js for reference        - Testnet: 0xCBfA..., 0x67eD..., 0xD1a7..., etc.        - Mainnet: 0x567c..., 0x58ec..., 0x6300..., 0x8d95...
